1.	Problem Statement: 
•	Monitoring system resources manually or using complex tools can be challenging for developers and users.
•	There is a need for a simple, real-time, and visually intuitive dashboard to monitor system performance. 
 
2.	Project Overview:  
This project provides a real-time dashboard to visualize system metrics:
•	CPU Usage
•	Memory Usage
•	Network Activity
•	Disk Usage
•	Process Count 
 
3.	Goals: 
•	Build a lightweight system monitoring tool
•	Use Python libraries for backend and visualization
•	Display real-time data refresh every second
•	Provide clear and interactive visuals
